Class Locations

java.lang.Object
  project3.three.Locations
Direct Known Subclasses:
LocationsAndValue
public class Locations
extends java.lang.Object

For every variable in a predicate list we need to store the locations of where that variable appears (there can be more than one). 

 Domain Definition:
     locations : Set<Location> -- the locations where a variable appears

 Instance Invariant:
     locations ≠ null
Last Modified: 21 Feb 2006

Version:
